Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:15.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:36.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:44.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:52.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:02:00.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:08.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:14.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:15.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:22.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:25.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:36.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:44.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:52.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:02:00.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:08.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:14.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現我的願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳  諾艾爾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:28.59,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(32,270)}「兩人的約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋兩個夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半熟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}關於來年飛碟應對費的上漲  預算委員會今早…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還穿著這身不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被爸爸這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕得及的話倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕得及…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是開學典禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  現在才八月份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比東京要早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小學時是一樣的  我以為妳知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼久的事情我怎麼會記得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩把麵包烤上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古宮乃乃香  還請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容再多一些不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋都已經全熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說「隨妳」的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來找妳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這個時間了  因為爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍後再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到迷路的孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳不是觀光客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是剛剛搬過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經知道分到哪個班了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少有人在這個小鎮上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在一個班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是古宮乃乃香  還請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  大家要成為好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宮同學  妳的座位在第二列的最後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢碰到  絕對饒不了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然聽見了  至少給個回應什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我們在湖邊見過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道為什麼妳說了那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宮同學  一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我乃乃香就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也叫我小春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳家住在湖邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確說是在山那邊  離湖還是有點距離的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有今天早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才說的是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  妳是搬到霧彌湖町來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之快來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  水坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是怎麼想的  我想問個明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡還是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只飛碟！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩  要兩杯薑汁汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香也喝這個可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…剛才說到哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續那個話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊  這很重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要激動  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許妳不知道  七年前可是引起了很大的轟動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞上有播  我還有些印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那個時候我正好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是當事者的話  就一定有不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟忽然降臨  就那樣架在湖上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是居然誰都沒有放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看  飲料來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為那個飛碟  麻煩才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  把我的也喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並沒有打擾到小鎮上的人們  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年了  看起來只是漫不經心地浮在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道背地裡在幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鎮的安全一天天被威脅著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁為時未晚  不做些什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得小鎮本身就代表著安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟和煩惱中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香選擇哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是煩惱中的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了恢復小鎮的和平而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(320,50,320,65)\bord0\1c000000\fs30\t(\fs27)}反對飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起恢復小鎮的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鎮的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  乃乃香也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要叫名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大聲喊出來  是傳達不出去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  這樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把飛碟從小鎮趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的小鎮不需要飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅趕之計  刻不容緩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要持續到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到飛碟消失為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以把它驅趕出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢  兩位顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是…必要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是道歉為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行B計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我們又沒有…做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  好好把話說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春的脾氣我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳能一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是順勢跟來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就開始下一項作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一項？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,26)\1cE7E7E7\3c2F2F2F\fs18\frz5.5\fscx95}飛碟應對科
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於飛碟的事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請先填一下這張表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想直接和飛碟的負責人對話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡管事的人給我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接和管事的人對話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和管事的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把管事的人叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便妳在窗口叫  管事的人也不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座島  以前是可以坐遊輪過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是後來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是因為危險就禁止進入了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事  果然很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要把我們的小鎮奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  給妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要生柚季的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的心情我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在找什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這樣就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和湊太沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也和你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過妳不要給別人惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是些毫無意義的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是飛碟和那個人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訴諸武力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向島進發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這絕對不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做到這種程度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包拿上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…我一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在生我的氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問妳一件事可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼想把飛碟趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為七年前飛碟出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而讓一樣東西改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在也無法恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有煙火從湖面升起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然規模不是那麼壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但水面倒映出的煙火卻非常美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在已經不會再放了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來發射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  是會飛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射這枚火箭試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全飛不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起把飛碟趕出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不許做危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須再找些人來幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好遵守和媽媽的約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好好遵守了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的好女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不起精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼困擾的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾能幫上忙的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾能來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾要怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把飛碟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小鎮的上空趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香討厭飛碟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想為朋友做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳願意再給我一點時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就有三個人了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
